<Author>jiminlondon
<Content>Breakfast is good, everything else, less so... The breakfast here is indeed very good and possibly one of the best I have had in Spain (admittedly given the English appetite at breakfast that's not saying much!) However I agree with the other reviewers in that it is simply way too noisy- I stayed in a first floor room over the reception and could here people coming and going all night. Also I thought the rooms were a bit dirty (I was there for four nights and my towel was never changed) and I found it too far out of the city center... The staff were nice though... 
