<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Noisy Rooms We stayed at the Husa Arenas in Dec 2005. Staff were excellent, Food was good Rooms are very very noisy. Paper thin walls, you can hear people in next room talking, clearly. Bathroom ventilator shaft goes right through to bathroom next door and you can actually see into their bathroom!! When someone else in the hotel runs a bath everyone gets to hear it!!The noisiest room we've ever stayed in.Oh and the beds are rock hard.and its a very long way from the centre. 30mins on tube or 20 mins by taxi 
